graph LR
    ODH[ODH Model Controller]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    ODH -->|extends CRDs| KServe[KServe 0.14+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODH -->|creates Routes| OSRouter[OpenShift Router 4.x<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    ODH -.->|GPU inference| NIM[NVIDIA NIM<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|creates AuthPolicy| Istio[Istio 1.20+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|creates HTTPRoutes| GatewayAPI[K8s Gateway API v1beta1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODH -.->|autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODH -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    ODH -.->|sidecar integration| TrustyAI[TrustyAI]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|manages via UI| ODH
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| ODH

    %% External Services
    ODH -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage]
    ODH -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 6443/TCP]
    ODH -->|NGC integration| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>HTTPS/443]

    %% Metrics and Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| ODH

    %% Arrows for different dependency types
    style ODH fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Required
    style KServe fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OSRouter fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External Optional
    style NIM fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style GatewayAPI fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style KEDA fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style TrustyAI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000

    %% External Services
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style NGC fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend
        Required[Required Dependency]
        Optional[Optional Dependency]
        InternalODH[Internal ODH Component]
        ExternalSvc[External Service]
    end

    style Required fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Optional fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style InternalODH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style ExternalSvc fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
